						               													<description>Included in the expansion : &amp;#10;&amp;#10;6 New Bid Boards with 4 new Influential People to choose.&amp;#10;1 Overlay Building Board featuring Garden Asylum and Jail&amp;#10;2 New Player Colors (Black &amp;amp; Gray) and Screens&amp;#10;&amp;#10; 4 New Influential People and Abilities: &amp;#10;&amp;#10;Warden  - Four Support/Reclaim one token/Add an opponent's cube to jail.&amp;#10;Heretic  - One Force/One Blackmail/Influence Asylum.&amp;#10;Governor  - Influence any open Influence Space/Add any opponent's cube to any open space.&amp;#10;Anarchist  - Gain the reward in any other space.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The legitimate authorities have given way to mob rule &amp;mdash; it's anarchy!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Revolution! Anarchy includes a new board overlay, new bidding boards, and two new sets of player components, allowing you to play Revolution! with up to six people. With this expansion, you'll be able to force the Warden to throw your enemies in jail, blackmail the Heretic and take over the asylum, and bribe the Anarchist, whose effects change every turn!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
